Title: Apartment a short walk away from the airport
Host.Name: Hosted by Saad
SubDescription.Title: Entire rental unit in Marrakesh, Morocco
Description:
Discover your ideal haven in Marrakech, just 3 minutes from the airport by taxi. Our modern retreat combines comfort and warm hospitality for an enriching experience. Only a 10-minute taxi ride from Jamaa el Fena, immerse yourself in the vibrant life of the city right at our doorstep. Enjoy our garden and traditional design.

Please note, as per local law, like all hotels in Morocco, we cannot accommodate unmarried Moroccan couples.

Book for a hassle-free getaway!

The space
Indulge in our one-bedroom apartment, providing all the comforts for your stay. We provide bedding and towels for your convenience. Enjoy complimentary high-speed and reliable Wi-Fi. The fully equipped kitchen is perfect for meal preparation. Relax in the living room or savor fresh air in the garden. Television is also available. Our housekeeping ensures a hotel-quality clean before your arrival and after your departure, ensuring an impeccable stay.

Title: Comfort & Luxury Near All Attractions
Host.Name: Hosted by Meriem
SubDescription.Title: Entire condo in Marrakesh, Morocco
Description: Idealy located apartment, 3 min from Guéliz in the Mabrouka district, with essential shops, a garden, and sports fields. Free parking. 2 km from downtown, 4 km from the train station, 5.1 km from Jardin Majorelle, 6 km from Jemaa el-Fna, and 10 km from the airport. Fully equipped with Wi-Fi and Netflix, perfect for a tourist or business stay. NB: According to Moroccan law, unmarried couples (Moroccans) are not allowed.

SubDescription.Title: Entire rental unit in Marrakesh, Morocco
Description:
Enjoy your stay in a modern and well furnished apartment next to all the amenities of a new residence.
It has 1 bedroom equipped with 4K home theater, living room, bathroom, American kitchen and small terrace.

Marrakech will always welcome you. ☺️

In addition, a 5G internet connection is included during your stay.

The space
Spacious living room for 3 people, dining room available, cozy small terrace for breakfast, queen size bedroom with built-in home theater.

Guest access
The property is fully accessible to any guest following the House Rules.


There is FREE PARKING in the basement of the residence.

Other things to note
🚨🚨according to the law in force (Article 490 of the
moroccan penal code), any person of Moroccan nationality traveling accompanied by a person of different sex (couple) or within a group with persons of different sex must present a marriage certificate.
This law only applies to MOROCCANS.
€ Important to Know: Couples
unmarried Moroccans are not allowed in the apartment.
THIS LAW IS ONLY FOR
MOROCCAN.

🚨🚨In case of non-compliance with the house rules during the automatic eviction stay from the apartment with respect to the cancellation policy.

🚨🚨 Security camera in the hallways of the building and in front of the apartment door.

Guest ID verification at the entrance of the building at the time of check-in is required.

By booking the apartment, you agree that it is essential to send your passport photo and all guests that they will be staying in the apartment via chat
Airbnb before check-in .

Title: Serenity of Targa
Host.Name: Hosted by Hamza
SubDescription.Title: Entire rental unit in Marrakech, Morocco
Description:
Serenity of Targa is a modern, new and bright apartment, offering a beautiful view without vis-à-vis. Ideally located in a quiet area, this apartment combines comfort and quality, offering a peaceful setting for stays for families or groups of friends. Every detail has been thoughtfully thought out to ensure a pleasurable and relaxing experience.

The space
This apartment sleeps up to 5 guests, with 3 spacious bedrooms, a modern living room, a fully equipped kitchen, and two bathrooms. The setting is perfect for relaxing thanks to a cozy lounge, coffee area and friendly dining area. The apartment is air conditioned and has Wi-Fi for your convenience. All furniture is new and high quality. Close to amenities, it's a great choice to explore Marrakech while being away from the hustle and bustle.

Exceptional benefits:
3 bedrooms, one of which is multipurpose with workspace 🛏️
Modern living room with coffee area and lounge area 🛋️
Kitchen equipped for homemade meals 🍽️
High speed wifi and air conditioning for optimal comfort 🌬️
Quiet neighborhood 5 min drive to Carrefour Targa 🏡

Close to main attractions:
5 min from Carrefour Targa shopping center
18 min from Gueliz neighborhood
26 min from Jamaâ El-Fna
25 min to Airport
21 min from Jardin Majorel

Other things TO note:
- According to Moroccan law, unmarried Moroccan couples are not allowed to stay together in the apartment.
- A valid ID card or passport is required before entering the apartment (in addition to a marriage certificate for Moroccan couples).

HouseRules.Aditional:
Apartment House Rules:

Occupation:
The apartment is designed to accommodate a maximum of 5 people.

Specific Conditions:

According to Moroccan law, unmarried Moroccan couples are not allowed to stay together in the apartment.
A valid ID card or passport is required before entering the apartment (in addition to a marriage certificate for Moroccan couples).
Parties and Noise:
Parties and events are strictly prohibited. Please respect the peace of the neighborhood, especially between 11 p.m. and 8 a.m.

Cleanliness and Maintenance:
The apartment must be left in the condition in which you found it.

Pets:
All pets are prohibited.

Security:
Make sure to lock all doors and windows when leaving the apartment.
Do not leave candles or open flames unattended.

Damage and Issues:

Any damage must be reported immediately.
Please report any issues that occurred during your stay before your departure.

Title: Modernity and Moroccan charm not overlooked
Host.Name: Hosted by Hind
SubDescription.Title: Entire rental unit in Marrakesh, Morocco
Description:
Welcome to our peaceful and comfortable apartment located in the heart of Marrakech, next to the CTM bus station and 900 meters from the train station. it combines modernity and Moroccan decoration for an authentic stay. Enjoy an unobstructed view, equipped with everything you need: Wi-Fi, Smart TV, equipped kitchen, and a comfortable bed of 160 cm. The spacious living room with a sofa sleeps two extra people, providing comfortable accommodation for 4 people.

The space
My listing is a perfect fit for a couple of persons. It has an equipped kitchen with a gas hob, range hood, kettle, stove, pots, dishes, and WiFi.
And air conditioning in the bedroom ,
The bathroom comes with towels, soap, and more.

In addition, a Smart TV is available with a Netflix account and access to IPTV for your entertainment.

For check-in , your passport will be requested

presentation of a marriage certificate required for couples if one of them is Moroccan or Muslim as required by Moroccan law
forbidden to receive guests

Guest access
The entire apartment

Other things to note
1. If you arrive from another city without a vehicle, prefer the CTM bus company, located in front of the building, for your trip. This is a more convenient option than the train.

2. When I am away, the keys will be given to you by my friend who is present on site.

3. If you plan to arrive very early or late for check-in, a lockbox is on the 5th floor next to the apartment door

Title: Studio Gueliz | Downtown | WiFi | Modern
Host.Name: Hosted by Reda
SubDescription.Title: Entire rental unit in Marrakesh, Morocco
Description:
Discover comfort in this beautiful studio where tradition and modernity blend harmoniously. This studio, comprising one bedroom and one bathroom, is in a great location, steps away from cafes, restaurants, and other entertainment venues. You will be 10 minutes from the Medina and the famous Jemaa el-Fna square, for a total immersion in the unique atmosphere of Marrakech.

✔Free coffee
24/7 ✔ security
✔ Smart TV (IPTV)
✔Laundry
✔ Fully equipped kitchen

The space
The accommodation consists of:

- Bedroom 1:
~A large double bed, double closet

- Main room: A large living room.

- Kitchen: A modern and fully-equipped kitchen.

**Amenities**

✔Wi-Fi
✔ Smart TV
✔Bedding and towels.
Coffee ✔machine and kettle
✔Full dish service
✔Fridge and fridge
Fire ✔cookers and oven
✔Laundry
24/7 ✔ security with guest ID check
✔ Free parking in front of the building

Guest access
Our ideal location will allow you to discover the treasures of Marrakech, from the gardens of Majorelle to the lively souks.

What's nearby:
Marrakech ✔Railway Station
✔ The famous Mohamed VI Boulevard with its green spaces,
✔ Convenience stores,
✔ Banks,
✔ Fitness & SPA AREA,
✔ Cafes and restaurants...
✔ Plaza Mall
✔ M Avenue
✔ Menara Mall
✔ Carré Eden,
Aswak Assalam ✔ Supermarket

After a day of exploring, relax in the cozy living room, elegantly appointed bedroom.

Whether you're on a business trip or a family vacation, our apartment offers the perfect mix of modern comforts and traditional charm.

Other things to note
There is construction work on the street next door, possibility of noise during the day

The health, safety, and well-being of our guests are of paramount importance. For this reason, we use a thorough cleaning process after each checkout.
Don't hesitate to get in touch if you have any other questions.
If you need any additional amenities, we are at your disposal.

HouseRules.Aditional:
* It is strictly forbidden to smoke (cigarettes, Shisha etc...) inside the accommodation under penalty of a fine of 2500 mad.

* Maximum of 3 guests can sleep in the property.

* It is forbidden to accommodate people outside of your booking group in the accommodation. 

* The space must be kept in good condition throughout your stay. If necessary, our cleaning team is available for your use. (paid service)

* In case of property damage, breakage or problems related to electricity or plumbing, please let us know immediately to allow a quick response.

* Sex tourism is strictly forbidden under penalty of immediate eviction and prosecution.

* In the event of a serious accident or death in the accommodation, whatever the causes and circumstances, the host and the Owner cannot be held liable and the tenants waive their right to file a complaint or to request repairs or compensation.

* The apartment is located in a secure residence, with check of entrances by the residence's security team. 

* A check-in will be done on site: an ID will be required.

Title: Super Apartment 5 minutes from the train station
Host.Name: Hosted by Mamoun
SubDescription.Title: Entire rental unit in Marrakech, Morocco
Description:
Elegance and comfort define this small apartment jewel in Marrakech ideally located, 5 min from the train station and the center of Gueliz. With its refined design and neat decor, it offers a bright living room, a welcoming bedroom, a full kitchen, and a modern bathroom. Every detail has been carefully chosen to give you a chic and welcoming atmosphere and living space. Welcome to your oasis of tranquility within the ochre city.

The space
Our apartment has 1 bedroom with a king size bed, 1 bathroom equipped with a walk-in shower, and a large living room offering a sofa bed that can accommodate two people. The kitchen is well equipped with oven and microwave, fridge , washing machine and all the necessary appliances available. Take advantage of our amenities, namely: free parking, a Smart TV with Netflix and Amazon Prime, and access to high-speed wifi. In short, an ideal space to combine comfort and convenience during your stay.

Unmarried couples allowed regardless of their nationalities

Guest access
Self check-in system, easy, and safe

Check-in from 3 p.m.

Check-out no later than 12pm

Title: Villa Yaneema, Family-Friendly in Marrakech
Host.Name: Hosted by Anass
SubDescription.Title: Entire home in Marrakesh, Morocco
Description:
Welcome to Villa Yaneema!
Located in the heart of Targa, Marrakech, our beautiful villa is the perfect retreat for guests & families seeking comfort, relaxation, and convenience. Our home is designed to provide a warm and welcoming atmosphere, making it the ideal base for exploring all that Marrakech has to offer.

The space
Our villa is a stunning 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom property that sleeps more than 8 guests. The interior is tastefully decorated with a mix of modern and traditional elements, creating a cozy and inviting ambiance. The property features:
*Ground floor:
A spacious living area with comfortable seating, large flat-screen TV, and Wi-Fi connectivity
A fully-equipped kitchen with all appliances, including a refrigerator, stove, microwave, and dishwasher
A dining area with seating for 8 guests
*1st floor:
A comfortable primary bedroom with King size bed, en-suite bathroom and walk-in closet
A second bedroom with a queen size bed, en-suite bathroom and walk in closet
A third bedroom, with 2 small double beds, 2 small single beds, en-suite bathroom and walk in closet
A spacious living room with comfortable seating, large flat-screen TV, and Wi-Fi connectivity
*Outdoors:
The largest swimming pool in targa
Sunbeds
Outdoor shower
A pergola with an outdoor dining area
BBQ
Lush gardens
The gardener will access the villa every Tuesday, Thursday, and Saturday to water the garden and clean the pool.
Amenities:
Our property offers a range of amenities to ensure your stay is comfortable and enjoyable. These include:
Free Wi-Fi connectivity throughout the property
Flat-screen TVs with cable channels in the living areas and primary bedroom
Fully-equipped kitchen with all appliances
Laundry facilities with washing machine
Ironing board and iron
Towels and toiletries provided

Guest access
Welcome to your home away from home in the heart of Targa, Marrakech! As our valued guest, you will have full access to the entire villa, ensuring a comfortable and enjoyable stay. Here’s what you can expect:

Private Entrance: Enjoy complete privacy with your own entrance, allowing you to come and go as you please.

Spacious Living Areas: Relax in our open-concept living room, equipped with cozy seating, a flat-screen TV, and plenty of natural light.

Fully Equipped Kitchen: Feel free to whip up your favorite meals in our modern kitchen, which includes all the essentials.

Bedrooms: Each bedroom is designed for your comfort, featuring plush bedding, ample storage, and beautiful decor. Fresh linens and towels are provided for your convenience.

Outdoor Space: Step outside to enjoy our private patio & garden area, perfect for morning coffee or evening relaxation. You’ll find outdoor seating and a BBQ grill for your use.
The gardener will access the villa every Tuesday, Thursday, and Saturday to water the garden and clean the pool.

Amenities: Take advantage of our complimentary Wi-Fi, air conditioning, and laundry facilities.

Parking: Free parking is available on the premises for your convenience.

We want you to feel at home during your stay, so please don’t hesitate to reach out if you have any questions or need assistance. Enjoy your stay!

Other things to note
Policies:
Please note that our property has the following policies:
Check-in time: 15:00
Check-out time: 11:00
Minimum stay: 2 nights
Maximum number of guests: 10
No smoking inside the villa or pets allowed
The gardener will access the villa every Tuesday, Thursday, and Saturday to water the garden and clean the pool.

House Rules:
We kindly ask that you respect the following house rules:
No loud noise after 10pm
No parties or events without prior approval
Respect the property's belongings and furnishings
Keep the property clean and tidy

Reviews:
Don't just take our word for it! Our previous guests have left us wonderful reviews, praising our comfortable home, convenient location, and excellent customer service. We're confident you'll have a wonderful stay with us!
We look forward to welcoming you to Villa Yaneema!

HouseRules.Aditional:
The gardener will access the villa every Tuesday, Thursday, and Saturday to water the garden and clean the pool. 

Respect the property: Guests are expected to treat the property with respect and care, including not damaging or removing any part of the property.

Keep noise levels down: Guests are expected to keep noise levels down after 10 PM and respect other neighbors nearby.

No parties: No parties or gatherings are allowed at the property without prior approval from the host.

No subletting: Guests are not allowed to sublet or rent out the property to others without prior approval from the host.

No illegal activities: Guests are not allowed to engage in illegal activities, such as drug use or prostitution, on the property.

Taxis are widely available in the area.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eCar Rentals: If you prefer to drive, we will be happy to advise on trusted car rentals nearby.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eParking: If you’re driving, ample street parking is available on and outside the villa.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eWe want you to have a seamless experience getting around, so don’t hesitate to reach out if you have any questions!"}]

SubDescription.Title: Entire rental unit in Marrakesh, Morocco
Description:
Welcome to This brand new well-equipped apartment with 2 bedrooms living room bathroom and well-equipped kitchen is an offer for your holidays or business trips. Its location allows you to shine on Marrakech in Bassatine Targa
This home is:
- Close to (gym ,hammam spa , traditional hammam,coffee snack pizza 2 min walk and 10-15 min to the city center gueliz and 18 min to djemaa lafna with your car or taxi or app indrive

The space
The accommodation: with high-speed fiber optic wifi &netflix&tv box
✅a large bed so you can sleep peacefully during your stay
Wide screen ✅TV with Netflix and tv box
✅2 bed 190/90
✅sofa bed in the living room

✅FULLY EQUIPPED KITCHEN:oven , coffee machine, electric oven, refrigerator, washing machine, household utensils,stovetop etc.

✅Bathroom EQUIPPED with HOT WATER and towels

✅FREE PARKING

Guest access
The whole accommodation

Other things to note
NB: According to Moroccan law, I do not accept unmarried Moroccan couples

Title: Modern studio near the airport
Host.Name: Hosted by Saad
SubDescription.Title: Entire rental unit in Marrakesh, Morocco
Description:
Welcome to Marrakech🌴! Our studio, just 3 min from the airport by taxi, is perfect for your late arrival or early check-out.

Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, you can relax after a long trip, while being 20 minutes from the bustling heart of Marrakech.

With flexible check-in from 2pm, no need to stress because of flight schedules! Enjoy the tranquility of Marrakech in a modern and warm setting

The space
🏠 Welcome to our studio in Marrakech! 🏠

Nestled in a peaceful and secure neighborhood, our studio is the perfect getaway for travelers looking for comfort and convenience. Here's what you can expect during your stay:

🛌 Spacious room: Our cozy room includes two beds and two L-shaped sofas, offering ample space to relax. You will also find a TV for your moments of entertainment.

Well-equipped 🍽️ kitchenette: Prepare your favorite meals in our fully equipped kitchenette. Whether you're making a quick breakfast or cooking a Moroccan feast, you'll find everything you need at your fingertips.

Modern 🚿 bathroom: Relax and cool off in our modern bathroom, equipped with a refreshing shower and quality amenities.

Free 📶 WiFi: Stay connected with our free WiFi, available throughout the studio for you to work, browse the internet, or stay connected with friends and family.

Free 🅿️ parking: Park your vehicle with peace of mind with our free onsite parking, offering extra convenience for guests with their own vehicle.

Flexible 🔑 check-in: Our flexible check-in from 2pm gives you the freedom to check in at any time of day, making it the ideal solution for late arrivals or for guests looking to check in early.

Book now and discover everything our studio has to offer during your upcoming stay in Marrakech

Guest access
I want to be on site to welcome you and give tips to help you

Other things to note
🔍 Other important details 🔍

We are delighted to host you in our studio in Marrakech for a memorable experience. We would like to respectfully inform you that, according to local law, unmarried Moroccan couples cannot be accepted into our property, as is the case in all hotels in the country. We appreciate your understanding in this regard.

If you have any questions or concerns about this policy please do not hesitate to contact us. We are here to help you plan a comfortable and enjoyable stay in Marrakech

Title: Central apartment with A/C and parking
Host.Name: Hosted by Yasmina
SubDescription.Title: Entire rental unit in Marrakesh, Morocco
Description:
This new apartment is central . It is 3 min from the center of the Hivernage district, 5 min from the center of Gueliz, 4 min from the train station, 12 min from the airport.
It is composed of a bright bedroom and living room, dining room, equipped kitchen (coffee machine) and balcony. Air conditioning is centralized.
The apartment is cozy, contemporary and has a parking space in the basement, it is ideal for both a business trip and a tourist stay.

The space
Composed of a bedroom with a double bed 200x180 cm and a living room with a sofa bed, you will be a few hundred meters from all the points of interest of Marrakech.

Title: Chic Daily Oasis
Host.Name: Hosted by Abdo
SubDescription.Title: Entire condo in Marrakesh, Morocco
Description:
Relax in this quiet and elegant space.

Guest access
The whole apartment

Other things to note
1. Respect for neighbours and calm:
• Quiet hours must be strictly observed (usually 10:00 - 08:00).
• It is forbidden to play music or make excessive noise that may disturb the neighborhood.
2. Friendliness and respect for the building:
• Thank you for respecting the rules of the listing and other occupants.
• It is strictly forbidden to hold parties and loud gatherings.
3. Guests and visitors:
• Any additional person not mentioned in the reservation must be pre-approved.
• The apartment is not suitable for events or gatherings that do not comply with applicable conditions. We do not accept Moroccan husbands and even friends of the other Moroccan sex

Failure to comply with these rules may result in penalties, including cancellation of a reservation without a refund.

Title: Cosy Apartment. Fiber Optic 5 min from Guéliz
Host.Name: Hosted by Anass
SubDescription.Title: Entire rental unit in Marrakesh, Morocco
Description:
Cozy apartment on the 1st floor, comprising 2 bedrooms and equipped with fiber optic. Conveniently located just 5 minutes from downtown Guéliz. Great for a comfortable and connected stay

The space
Welcome to our cozy 1st floor apartment, ideally located just 5 minutes from downtown Guéliz. This place is perfect for a comfortable and convenient stay in Marrakech.

The apartment has 2 comfortable bedrooms: one bedroom with a double bed and one bedroom with two separate beds, each carefully arranged to guarantee your rest. The living room is equipped with air conditioning, offering a cool and inviting space to relax in front of the smart TV.

For your meals, a well-equipped kitchen is at your disposal, with all the essentials to prepare your favorite dishes, including a coffee machine. The dining area can accommodate up to 4 people, perfect for dinners for families or groups of friends.

A workspace is also available, ideal for professionals or those who want to stay connected thanks to high-speed fiber optic. A washing machine is also available for your convenience.

The bathroom includes a toilet, adding to your comfort.

We've thought of all the details to make you feel at home, whether you're traveling for work or on vacation. Enjoy our central location and all the modern amenities we offer.

Other things to note
Our concierge services in Marrakech

To make your stay even more enjoyable, we offer a range of personalized concierge services upon request:

Airport ✈️ Transfers: Organization of your trips to and from Marrakech airport.
Private 🚐 transportation: Providing private vans for your trips in or around the city.
🚗 Car rental: Explore Marrakech and its surroundings at your own pace with our rental vehicles.
🏞️ Excursions: Explore beautiful destinations, such as Agafay, Ourika, and Essaouira.
🏍️ Activities: Enjoy a memorable experience with activities like ATV, camel rides, hot air balloons, and waterkarting.
These services and activities are available on request and can be adapted to suit your desires. Feel free to contact us to organize these unique moments and make your stay exceptional!

HouseRules.Aditional:
We kindly ask you to respect the following rules during your stay in our apartment, to ensure a pleasant and safe experience for everyone:

Extra guests

Guests outside of the people mentioned in the reservation are not allowed to access the apartment without prior agreement. Any request to add guest(s) must be made in advance and approved by the host.

Unmarried Moroccan couples are not accepted in the accommodation.

Respect for tranquility

It is strictly forbidden to bring local people (local girls) into the accommodation.

Smoking

Smoking is not allowed inside the apartment.
Smoking is only allowed on the terrace or balcony. 

Please be respectful to other occupants and do not dispose of cigarette butts or trash.

Respectful behavior

We ask that you respect the neighborhood and maintain calm and respectful behavior.

Safety and Amenities

The residence is secured 24 hours a day, and we kindly ask you to respect the safety rules in force, in particular regarding access to the swimming pool and basement parking.

House amenities should be used with care. 

Respect for the environment

Please respect the environment by saving water and electricity during your stay.

Title: Cozy apartment near train station
Host.Name: Hosted by Khalil
SubDescription.Title: Entire rental unit in Marrakesh, Morocco
Description:
Immerse yourself in the warm atmosphere of this carefully decorated apartment with a Berber theme, combining tradition and modernity for a unique stay in Marrakech.

5 min drive to train station and M Avenue (15 min walk)
Only 50m from Aswak Salam

Elegant Berber decor: an authentic and refined interior
Netflix included: for relaxing evenings after a day of exploring
WiFi / Iptv
Air conditioning

This apartment offers all the comforts for a pleasant stay.

Other things to note
Building without elevator

SubDescription.Title: Entire condo in Marrakesh, Morocco
Description:
Welcome to this magnificent exclusive apartment in Abwab Guéliz 2 in Marrakech. Bright and facing south, it combines modernity and Moroccan traditions. Composed of an air-conditioned Moroccan living room with Berber touches, a living room opening onto an equipped kitchen, an intimate master bedroom, a children's bedroom with two beds, and a bathroom with separate WC. Carefully decorated and highlighting local craftsmanship, it offers comfort and authenticity for an unforgettable stay.

The space
My accommodation, fully exposed to the south, is bathed in natural light throughout the day. Each room has a large window facing the street, offering a pleasant and sunny space. The living room is spacious and pleasant, the kitchen is fully equipped and the room is comfortable and bright. The bathroom, modern and well ventilated, complete with warm and welcoming.

HouseRules.Aditional:
House Rules of the Property:

Welcome to our home! In order to ensure a pleasant stay for all and to respect the premises as well as the neighborhood, we kindly ask you to follow the following rules:

1. Respect for the Property

Please treat this home like it's your own.

Any damage or damage must be reported immediately.

Furniture and equipment should be used with care and left in the original condition.

2. Smoking

Strictly no smoking inside the listing.

Please only smoke outside and throw your cigarette butts in an ashtray provided for this purpose.

3. Respect for the Neighborhood

Neighbors' peace and quiet must be respected at all times.

No excessive noise after 10pm.

Parties and loud gatherings are not allowed.

4. Number of Guests

The space is designed for up to 5 people.

No additional visitors are allowed without prior approval.

5. Use of Spaces

The living room and living room must be used with respect for the premises.

The master bedroom is intended for 2 people maximum.

The children's room is equipped with 2 single beds and should not accommodate more than 2 children.

6. Maintenance and Cleanliness

Please keep the premises clean and dispose of the trash in the planned garbage cans.

The property must be left in good condition upon departure.

7. Safety

Always close doors and windows when leaving the listing.

No valuables should be left unattended.

8. Non-Respect Penalties

Violation of these rules may result in security deposit deduction and/or cancellation of the stay without refund.

Thank you for your understanding and kind cooperation to make sure your stay goes smoothly!

Enjoy your stay and stay!

Title: Luxury apartment PIS
Host.Name: Hosted by Jawad
SubDescription.Title: Entire rental unit in Marrakech, Morocco
Description:
-Bel new apartment, close to the city center
(Gueliz), in a modern and secure residence.

10min in Gueliz / 20min a jemaa el fna / 20min to the airport / 15min for quad bikes

-We can arrange transport from the airport to the apartment to facilitate your hassle-free check-in for only 15euro ( but if you are more than 4 people We have to provide you with two cars at €35) Knowing that taxi rates €15

The space
The apartment is all set up and
comfortable.

V NEAR THE CITY CENTER
V POOL( )
V SPACIOUS
V AIR-CONDITIONING
V WiFi
V SMART TV
V NETFLIX
V EQUIPPED KITCHEN
V WASHING MACHINE
V SECURE RESIDENCE 24/7
V camera for your safety in front of the door of the apartment

-THEAPARTMENT is very clean. A service from
cleaning is scheduled before your arrival.

-Chers guests, please fill out the personal information form with the caretaker of the residence upon your arrival.

-PS: Unmarried foreign couples allowed to book ( by Moroccan law)
But forbidden 🚫 for unmarried Arab couples.

Other things to note
- Breakfast is paid. (€7 per person if you have 4 or more /€10 person if you are 3 or less )

- Breakfast contains:
olive eye, egg , butter , honey , cheese, bread , Moroccan mssemen, tea, coffee, juice , Moroccan cake

- but if you want something special you can tell me and I'll add it for you , as long as you pay an extra price

HouseRules.Aditional:
Extra rules
IMPORTANT: We would like to inform our dear customers that:

- For Moroccan couples/Arab nationalities,( or mixed (if one of the spouses is of Moroccan/ Arab nationality) a marriage certificate is mandatory and must be presented at check-in.

- Sex tourism is strictly prohibited under penalty of immediate expulsion and prosecution.

 - You are asked to adopt a good attitude towards the neighborhood (quiet hours between 23:00 and 8:00) and to respect local customs and customs. Parties and other events are not permitted.

- In the event of failure to comply with the nuisance rules, our agency reserves the right to expel tenants before the end of their stay.

- Any additional guests must be declared to the host.

- Only families, married couples or foreign couples and unbiased groups are allowed in our accommodation, according to the rules governing the residence. (Required foreign passports for unmarried couples, or marriage certificate for married couples in case of Arab nationality) 

- Regarding the use of the pool and balconies, the tenant is responsible for his family and children, the Agency waives all liability in case of negligence on the part of the Tenant.

- Pool times are: 9am-1pm and 3pm-7pm.

-For the pool 4 bracelets available ,"In case of loss of pool bracelets, you will be charged a fine of €30. So please keep them carefully 🙏 to avoid any additional fees.”

Title: Quiet apartment
Host.Name: Hosted by Sohayb
SubDescription.Title: Entire rental unit in Marrakesh, Morocco
Description:
Offering a view of a quiet street, this modern apartment in Nubie features 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a fully equipped kitchen, and a comfortable living/dining room. Free Wi-Fi and Netflix included. Ideal for relaxing or working remotely. The apartment is located 6.2 km from the airport, 6.4 km from the train station, 6.5 km from the Menara Garden, 6.3 km from the Majorelle Garden, and 7.6 km from the Yves Saint Laurent Museum.

The space
Welcome to my warm and modern apartment located in a neighborhood close to all commercial amenities. The accommodation is spacious and bright, offering all the necessary comfort for a pleasant stay.

• Living Room: A large living space with a comfortable Moroccan-style seating area, a flat-screen TV, and a coffee table. Ideal for relaxing after a day of sightseeing.
• Kitchen: Fully equipped kitchen with a refrigerator, oven, electric kettle, washing machine, and all the basic utensils to prepare your meals.
• Bedroom: Main bedroom with a double bed, bed linens provided, and storage spaces for your belongings.
• Second Bedroom: A bedroom with a single bed, bed linens provided, and storage spaces for your belongings.
• 2 Bathrooms: Both modern bathrooms feature a shower, sink, and toilet. Towels and basic products are provided.

Title: Appartement cosy
Host.Name: Hosted by Hicham
SubDescription.Title: Entire rental unit in Marrakesh, Morocco
Description:
Good evening, everyone!
We are super happy to introduce you to our apartment , a little corner of heaven that we have arranged with a lot of love. Here, everything has been thought out to make you feel at home (but better!):
Great place to disconnect, relax and fully enjoy the magical atmosphere of Marrakech We look forward to welcoming you and sharing this place that is important to us.

Other things to note
Marrakech, Marrakech-Safi, Morocco
In this neighborhood you will find in the immediate vicinity pharmacies, banks for your withdrawals and exchanges, as well as restaurants and bakeries. Public transport (buses, taxis) pass in front of the building. The neighborhood is lively day and night, with shops open until late at night (after midnight) and very early in the morning.
Getting around
My apartment has a prime location on a large boulevard, offering you direct and easy access to public transport. Just get off the building to find yourself in the middle of the boulevard, where you will find a bus stop with regular passages every 15 minutes. This bus will take you directly to the city center and Jemaa el-Fna square. In addition, large and small taxis are also available nearby for your trips to other destinations and spend day and night.
For those traveling by car, secure and free parking is available inside the residence and also in front of the door of the building. This service is included in the price of your reservation.

SubDescription.Title: Entire rental unit in Marrakesh, Morocco
Description: Discover our cozy apartment, located in the Targa neighborhood, just a 15 minute drive to downtown. This beautiful apartment offers **2 spacious bedrooms **, a large living room and a modern American kitchen. Perfect for families, it also features a secure children's pool and a gated residence for your tranquility. Enjoy a pleasant and secure stay with us!

Title: New! Modern Appart, Parking , piscine & Fiber wifi
Host.Name: Hosted by Anass
SubDescription.Title: Entire condo in Marrakesh, Morocco
Description:
Immerse yourself in the elegance of this luxurious family apartment, ideally located for an unforgettable stay in Marrakech. Enjoy a refined setting where comfort and serenity meet, with stunning views of the pool without vis-à-vis, guaranteeing total privacy.

- 7 minutes from the airport
- 3 min to M Avenue and train station
- 10 min from the Medina and Jemaa el-Fna

The space
✔ 2 spacious bedrooms: Queen size bed and 2 separate beds, perfect for families or groups of friends.
Secured ✔ pool: Relax in the sunshine of Marrakech.
✔ Private parking in the basement: Secure and convenient for your vehicle.
✔ Great location:
- 7 minutes from the airport
- 3 min to M Avenue and train station
- 10 min from the Medina and Jemaa el-Fna
Modern ✔ amenities: Air conditioning, fiber wifi (100 Mbps), Smart TV with IPTV, fully equipped kitchen.
✔ 2 private balconies: Enjoy a pleasant view of the pool.

Perfectly located close to supermarkets, restaurants and shops, this apartment is your oasis of tranquility in the heart of the city. Book now for a memorable stay in Marrakech!

HouseRules.Aditional:
We kindly ask you to respect the following rules during your stay at our Villa , in order to ensure a pleasant and safe experience for everyone:

Extra guests

Guests outside of the people mentioned in the reservation are not allowed to access the villa without prior agreement. Any request to add guest(s) must be made in advance and approved by the host.

Unmarried Moroccan couples are not accepted in the accommodation.

Respect for tranquility

It is strictly forbidden to bring local people (local girls) into the accommodation.

Smoking

No smoking inside the Villa .
Smoking is only allowed on the terrace or garden . 

Please be respectful to other occupants and do not dispose of cigarette butts or trash.

Respectful behavior

We ask that you respect the neighborhood and maintain calm and respectful behavior.

House amenities should be used with care. 

Respect for the environment

Please respect the environment by saving water and electricity during your stay.

Title: New apart in gueliz (Fiber Wi-Fi/ Pool/Parking)
Host.Name: Hosted by Mohamed
SubDescription.Title: Entire rental unit in Marrakesh, Morocco
Description:
New apartment in Guéliz, 2 min from Marrakech train station and M Avenue. Located in a secure residence with swimming pool, it offers 2 bedrooms a modern living room, a dining room, an equipped kitchen, a bathroom and 2 separate toilets.
Enjoy 2 terraces, air conditioning, IPTV Smart TV, fiber wifi and free parking.

⚠️ Important notice:
Unmarried local couples or local/foreign mixed couples are not allowed to stay due to local regulations.

The space
Modern and Refined Apartment in Guéliz – Pool, Terraces and High Speed Wi-Fi

Treat yourself to a unique experience in this stylish and bright apartment, located on the 2nd floor of a secure residence with swimming pool in the heart of Guéliz. Just 2 minutes from Marrakech train station, M Avenue, and close to the popular Hivernage district, this apartment has a great location to explore the city while enjoying a peaceful setting.
Listing composition:

Master bedroom: Queen bed, neat decoration and relaxing atmosphere.
Second bedroom: Two single beds, perfect for kids or friends.
Modern living room: Warm atmosphere with traditional Moroccan touches.
Dining room: Spacious table for 6 people, ideal for meals for families or groups of friends.
Fully equipped kitchen: Refrigerator, microwave, coffee machine, kettle and everything you need to cook.
Bathroom: Modern shower and separate toilet for optimal comfort.

🌟 Stylated apartment in Coeur de Guéliz 🌟
Live a unique experience in this chic and modern apartment, just a 15-minute walk from Carré Eden and 10 minutes from M Avenue. Ideally located close to the train station, this apartment offers a perfect combination of comfort, convenience and style.

Apartment 🏠 features:
📍 Privileged location – Close to main attractions, shops and restaurants.
🏊 Access to the Commune Pool – An oasis of freshness just steps away.
Spacious 🌞 Layout – An open, airy, and comfortable living space.
❄️ Air conditioning – Stay cool even on the hottest days.
High Speed 📶 WiFi – Fast, reliable internet.
📺 Smart TV with Netflix – Relax with your favorite movies and shows.
Fully Equipped 🍽️ Kitchen – Make it easy to cook your meals.
Private 🌅 Balcony – Enjoy fresh air and nice views.
Free 🚗 Parking – Convenient parking spot included.
🧺 Washer – Great for extended stays.
24/7 🔐 security – Safe and secure environment.
☕ Breakfast Available – On request, with extra charge.

⚠️ Important notice:
Unmarried local couples or local/foreign mixed couples are not allowed to stay due to local regulations.

Why choose this apartment?
With its modern design, quality amenities and central location, this apartment is perfect for stays with family, friends or professionals. Come and experience an unforgettable stay in Marrakech, where comfort, modernity and serenity meet.

We look forward to hosting you and helping make your stay exceptional!

Guest access
Guests enjoy exclusive access to the entire apartment, including a private terrace and all the facilities of the secure residence. Enjoy modern amenities, like the fully equipped kitchen and cozy living room. I am at your disposal for any questions or assistance in order to make your stay as pleasant as possible.

Other things to note
Our Concierge Services in Marrakech

In order to enrich your stay in Marrakech, we offer you a selection of tailor-made concierge services, available on request:

Airport ✈️Transfers: Organization of your trips to and from Marrakech airport.
Private 🚘transportation: Providing private vehicles for your trips in or around town.
🚙Car rental: Discover Marrakech and its surroundings at your own pace with our rental vehicles.
Excursions: Embark on an adventure to splendid destinations such as Agafay, Ourika, or Essaouira.
🪂Activities: Experience unforgettable moments with experiences like ATV, camel rides, hot air balloons and waterkarting.

All of these services are customizable and can be adapted to suit your wishes. Contact us to host these unique experiences and make your stay a great one!

Title: Beautiful T3 close to train station
Host.Name: Hosted by Mohamed
SubDescription.Title: Entire rental unit in Marrakesh, Morocco
Description:
Discover this modern T3 apartment ideally located in Guéliz, 5 minutes from the train station and Carré Eden, and 10 minutes from Menara Mall. This apartment combines comfort and elegance, with its 2 spacious bedrooms, bright living room, and beautifully equipped kitchen. Located in a very secure building, enjoy a pleasant living environment close to all amenities: restaurants, cafes, shops and more. Whether you're traveling for work or on vacation.

The space
Welcome to this modern and luxurious T3 apartment in the heart of Guéliz! 🌟

Ideally located, you will be only 5 minutes from the train station🚉, perfect for your trips, and 5 minutes to Carré Eden🛍️, where you will find many restaurants 🍽️ like Café La Flamme or Kechmara to enjoy excellent culinary experiences. 10 minutes from Menara Mall🏬, you'll have access to various shops and leisure activities, as well as the famous Entrepotes restaurant.

The accommodation is also close to the Medina 🕌 (about 15 minutes by car), where you can explore the souks and discover the authentic charm of Marrakech. You will also find the Jardin Majorelle 🌿 10 minutes away, a must-see place to recharge your batteries in the city.

The apartment has two spacious and luxurious bedrooms🛏️, elegantly decorated to ensure a comfortable stay. The living room is bright and modern🛋️, perfect for relaxing after a busy day. The equipped kitchen allows 🍳 you to prepare delicious meals, or you can opt for one of the many restaurants nearby.

Located in a modern and secure building, this apartment is the perfect place to fully enjoy Marrakech with comfort and style✨.

Other things to note
"According to Moroccan laws, unmarried Moroccan couples are not allowed in this property. Thank you very much for your understanding.”
